article.description: Tyler Cheese had 20 points as Akron beat Merrimack 64-47 on Friday night.
article.headline: Cheese scores 20 to lift Akron over Merrimack 64-47
article.linkText: Cheese scores 20 to lift Akron over Merrimack 64-47
article.story: AKRON, Ohio -- Tyler Cheese had 20 points as Akron beat Merrimack 64-47 on Friday night. Xeyrius Williams had 14 points, 12 rebounds and four blocks for Akron (5-2), which earned its fifth consecutive home victory. Channel Banks added 11 points. Jaleel Lord had 11 points for the Warriors (5-4). Juvaris Hayes added 10 points. Jordan Minor had eight rebounds. Akron matches up against Marshall on the road on Wednesday. Merrimack matches up against Brown on the road on Wednesday. --- More AP college basketball: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and https://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
